name: Ying Yang Go
description:
I completely forgot about the jam and made this game in 1,5 hours.. :( Hope it is enjoyable.

Press space to separate Ying and Yang, and press "A" and "D" keys to go left and right. Run from incoming red enemies using your Ying-Yang symbol, and separate Ying and Yang to gain triple points.
